Graphics gurus - could Mythic just generate a second set of graphics primitives that they could give us to optionally use?<br>
  <br>
These prims would be much less complex, maybe not just colored cubes, but a lot simpler polygon-wise than what we have now?  To my simple mind, it seems like that could be almost drop in to the existing engine, and could easily be set up to make it our option at startup what to use.<br>
